		      <li>Students having a guaranteed and secured work placement before arrival.<br></li>
		      <li>Self-placement: Students have flexibility in finding and locating a job independently. The only requirement is that the students must provide CSB with a copy of their employment agreement (job offer).<br></li>
		      <li>CSB-placement: CSB has made arrangements with several companies throughout the United States to allow us to fill their positions with Work and Travel students. We will arrange a basic, entry-level or seasonal-work job, much like one a student in the United States would have during the school vacation.<br></li>
